setRecipient.t.sol
├── when new recipient is the same as the old recipient
│   ├── it should update the recipient (even if it's the same)
│   └── it should emit an RecipientUpdated event
├── when new recipient is different from the old recipient
│   ├── it should update the recipient
│   └── it should emit an RecipientUpdated event
└── when user already has custom recipient set
    ├── it should update the recipient to the new value
    └── it should emit an RecipientUpdated event with the correct old and new recipients
